video_title: Resolve || DreamSMP Animatic
description:
Hi. I recommend watching "Desolate" again before you see this one so you have an idea of where I left off. I wanted someone to be able to watch all three in a row and have them link up timeline-wise.

Song this time around is "Line of Sight" by ODESZA. I had a few others I was tossing around but this is the one that stuck. I really hope you enjoy this one, these big projects are very draining. On that note, I think I'm gonna take a break from making these huge animatics...

My plan moving forward is this:

Livestreaming - In a day or so I'd like to do a livestream (at twitch.tv/late_august_) where I go over this animatic panel by panel. I think it will help me arrange my thoughts so that I can make a better process video. Coincidentally, my second item on the list is:

Process video - I said I wanted to do it and I still do, problem is that I'm not a great explainer when it comes to the creative process. I will try my best though.

Smaller projects - I have some ideas for a few DreamSMP projects that will (hopefully) take less time and will allow me to try out new styles and editing techniques

Personal projects - I know it's not what you're here for, but I've got some original ideas that I'm excited about. Hope that's not too heartbreaking.

Here's some links to socials. I'm @late_august_ on almost everything. Follow me:
Instagram - https://instagram.com/late_august_
Twitter - https://twitter.com/late_august_
Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/late_august_

Share the video around if you like it, it helps me a bunch. I don't make any money from these videos (any ads you see are put there by the record label that copyright claimed the video) so if you want to support me I have a venmo @late_august_ and a redbubble shop (redbubble.com/people/in-late-august). Prints and stickers for this animatic will be up soon.

video_title: They Told Us NOT To Do THIS | Cabin Build
description:
The 1 thing EVERYONE told us NOT to DIY in our cabin... and we're doing it üòú Dreaming of van life? For your chance to win a custom 4x4 Mercedes Sprinter Van and support a great cause go to http://omaze.com/eamonandbec

‚ñ∫ Our DELICIOUS Soup Recipe https://bit.ly/39wXmN8
‚ñ∫ SUBSCRIBE for a new video every single Sunday youtube.com/eamonbec
‚ñ∫ The vlog continues on Instagram https://instagram.com/eamonandbec‚Äã

We've escaped to the wilderness & we're building our home at a cabin in the woods. Now that we are dealing with the extreme cold temperatures of a Canadian winter we have moved our renovations to the indoors. This week we are tackling the 1 project absolutely EVERYBODY told us NOT to DIY: DRYWALL!! Wish us luck... I think we're gonna need it. 

Catch up on our cabin in the woods videos: https://bit.ly/3mNAcpX‚Äã

Who are we?

We're Eamon and Bec, a Canadian couple who previously lived and traveled full-time in our self converted Sprinter Van!! When the pandemic hit in 2020 we made the difficult decision to abandon our van in Africa and fly home to Canada. Now we're here... living at a cabin in the Canadian wilderness. We've always envisioned moving into the woods by the lake and building our dream tiny cabin as a home base for us to come back to in between our international travels.
